# SkythornLauncher graphics — hands off

Never modify, export, replace, copy over, or commit changes to graphics/assets unless the user **explicitly** asks (e.g. "update the backgrounds", "export buttons from PXZ").

## Protected by default

- `Assets/profiles-background.png`
- `Assets/settings-background.png`
- `Assets/home-background.png`
- Everything under `Assets/` (PNG, ICO, fonts used as art, menu button images)

## Allowed without asking

- Code/XAML that **references** existing asset paths (no file replacement)
- `publish.ps1` already preserves the two menu backgrounds; do not weaken that

## Forbidden unless explicitly requested

- Pulling art from PXZ, OneDrive, or other folders into `Assets/`
- Running or changing export scripts that write into `Assets/`
- Overwriting backgrounds during publish, build, or git operations

When in doubt, ask before touching any file under `Assets/`.
